OL,6,FA man who threatened to 'undermine'
OL,7,FLabour's Samantha Dixon in her role as
OL,8,FMP has been a handed jail sentence.
OL,10,FBenjamin Scott-Thrale, 32, from ,
OL,11,Ffirst contacted the City of Chester MP
OL,12,Fasking for help with a family problem
OL,13,Fin June 2023.
OL,15,FMrs Dixon told Scott-Thrale later that
OL,16,Fmonth, she could do nothing more to
OL,17,Fassist and that he should seek legal
OL,18,Fadvice.
