OL,6,FScott-Thrale began to harrass and
OL,7,Fstalk Mrs Dixon by making phone calls,
OL,8,Fsending emails and calling into her
OL,9,Fconstituency office.
OL,11,FThe police arrested and charged Scott-
OL,12,FThrale after he rang the MP's office
OL,13,Fagain on 30 January 2024, saying he
OL,14,Fwould continue to until he had a face
OL,15,Fto face meeting in which she helped
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,18,FHe was arrested and charged with
OL,19,Fstalking and harassment.
