OL,3,CMan given jail sentence for stalking
OL,4,Cand harassing MP
OL,6,FScott-Thrale said: "What's the
OL,7,Fdefinition of stalking? It involves a
OL,8,Fcourse of conduct against one person.
OL,9,FI haven't stalked one person."
OL,11,FScott-Thrale was found guilty and was
OL,12,Fgiven a six-week custodial sentence at
OL,13,FWarrington Magistrates' Court on 12
OL,14,FApril 2024.
OL,16,FThe jail sentence has been served
OL,17,Fafter he was already in custody. He
OL,18,Fmust also pay a victim surcharge of
OL,19,F#154.
