OL,3,CMan given jail sentence for stalking
OL,4,Cand harassing MP
OL,6,FSenior Crown Prosecutor Simon Green,
OL,7,Fof CPS Mersey Cheshire, said: "The
OL,8,FCrown Prosecution Service said that
OL,9,FBenjamin Scott-Thrale pursued a
OL,10,Fdeliberate and persistent campaign of
OL,11,Fstalking and harassment against his
OL,12,Flocal MP when he realised she couldn't
OL,13,Fgive him what he wanted.
OL,15,F"His constant emails, phone calls and
OL,16,Fvisits to the office were meant to
OL,17,Fthreaten her and leave her with the
OL,18,Fimpression that he was always there,
OL,19,Fin the background and would continue
OL,20,Fto be.
