OL,4,Cand harassing MP
OL,6,F"Requests from the MP and her staff to
OL,7,Fstop the contact and seek legal advice
OL,8,Fwere ignored as was the formal request
OL,9,Ffrom the police.
OL,11,F"His behaviour became criminal and the
OL,12,FCPS has successfully prosecuted him
OL,13,Ffor it.
OL,15,F"Members of Parliament perform a vital
OL,16,Frole in our democracy and it is
OL,17,Fessential that they are able to
OL,18,Frepresent their constituents without
OL,19,Ffear.
