OL,6,F"The prosecution of people who
OL,7,Fthreaten this is a key priority for
OL,8,Fthe CPS. Benjamin Scott-Thrale
OL,9,Fjeopardised that role and now has a
OL,10,Fcriminal record."
OL,12,FScott-Thrale must comply with a 12-
OL,13,Fmonth Post Sentence Supervision. The
OL,14,Fcourt also agreed to a two-year
OL,15,Frestraining order.
